  "title": "Introducing OpenConjecture, a living dataset of mathematics conjectures from the ArXiv",
  "dek": "We are releasing OpenConjecture, a dataset of 890 unproved conjectures from recent arXiv math papers. On a small subset, GPT-5.4 finds candidate proofs or counterexamples, and formalizes several in Lean.",
